Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 9/27/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez and the crew are in the studio talking about some of the biggest topics in hip hop and entertainment. They discuss Cardi B and Love & Hip Hop/rapper Akbar V's daylong back and forth on Twitter and subliminals between Nicki Minaj and the "Up" rapper, New York Giants loss over the Dallas Cowboys, Rachel Dolezal's OnlyFans leak, secret hustles, Popeyes vs Wingstop and more!

All that on top of your favorites such as Ride Or Die, Curved, and we even got a Guru update from 4 years ago!

All that and more on Ebro In The Morning!
